    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/3dbd7aca96b54bf2403cb3923e0360a4.poster.avif?t=1696816191\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/3dbd7aca96b54bf2403cb3923e0360a4.webm?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/3dbd7aca96b54bf2403cb3923e0360a4.mp4?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>《Hope's Final Defense》是一款动作 Roguelike 游戏，您可以在其中创建一套技能牌组来对抗成群的敌人。 从许多破坏游戏的物品和升级中进行选择。 打造强大的建筑并创造致命的协同效应来对抗来自 Negativia 的无尽怪物。 你能保护人类最后的希望吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/1c87a6ca07288d28278b8174db24389e.poster.avif?t=1696816191\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/1c87a6ca07288d28278b8174db24389e.webm?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/1c87a6ca07288d28278b8174db24389e.mp4?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制定毁灭性连击技能策略</h2>技能就像使用卡牌一样，可以创造出令人难以置信的连击。 制定如何安排技能以获得最大伤害的策略。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/f0c81f3e9685f4f6e562ddd597726554.poster.avif?t=1696816191\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/f0c81f3e9685f4f6e562ddd597726554.webm?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/f0c81f3e9685f4f6e562ddd597726554.mp4?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择升级和工艺物品</h2>每次运行都会提供不同的升级、物品和技能选择。 仔细选择，每次都能创造不同的组合和体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/7dcdad7559b4447bdcd9c0e2f4d7a37e.poster.avif?t=1696816191\" width=598 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/7dcdad7559b4447bdcd9c0e2f4d7a37e.webm?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/7dcdad7559b4447bdcd9c0e2f4d7a37e.mp4?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可定制的游戏风格</h2>用祝福塑造你的角色以适应不同的游戏风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/c832d855aea4878ba062d40b6d0ed5cc.poster.avif?t=1696816191\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/c832d855aea4878ba062d40b6d0ed5cc.webm?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379590/extras/c832d855aea4878ba062d40b6d0ed5cc.mp4?t=1696816191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>每个角色都是独一无二的，拥有自己的主动和被动技能，以及超过 35 种独特的升级。 即使拥有相同的技能，也可能有不同的玩法。<br></li><li>超过 20 个强大的物品可供组合。 每个效果都会改变你的构建方式。<br></li><li>许多独特的敌人都有自己的攻击方式。<br></li><li>你可以选择不同的英雄来玩，如果你不喜欢一个英雄，那就玩下一个吧！<br></li><li>克服一个困难后，您可以尝试下一个困难。</li></ul>",
